From d3a61f5b22024a0e604d49a7a4c2612bacc52cac Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: zqh923 <zhouqinghong1@hisilicon.com>
Date: Mon, 13 Oct 2025 21:19:41 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/9] [feat] basic modification for qwen3 moe

enable qwen3 attn dp+ep

eliminate rotary_emb index

enable gmm nz

topk fused

enable w8a8

qwen3 mtp

replace deepep

replace reshape and cache

[fix] max len padding bug

enable mtp load weights

[fix] get cos_sin from RotaryEmbedding

[fix] bf16 bug fix

[fix] mtp prefix

eliminate scatter element

mtp accuracy fix

cast smooth_scale_2 to float in gmm, as to  remove trans_cast

enable nz to gate and moe

Signed-off-by: zqh923 <zhouqinghong1@hisilicon.com>
